---
title: Parmesan Pan-Fried Chicken Breasts Gnocchi with Spinach and Peas
description: Golden, pan-fried gnocchi add a delicious twist to classic Alfredo! Rich cream and savoury Parmesan come together to make a luscious sauce for this any day of the week supper.
